Package: MultiRD
Type: Package
Title: Multi-robust deconvolution algorithm
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Chixiang Chen <chixiang.chen@pennmedicine.upenn.edu>
Maintainer: Chixiang Chen <chixiang.chen@pennmedicine.upenn.edu>
Description: MultiRD adopts a penalized regression scheme to incorporate multiple information into the deconvolution process of bulk RNA-seq data. The resulting algorithm is robust against incorrect marker genes, incorrect reference data, and incorrect extra information about the target bulk data (e.g., population-level cell proportions).  
License: Artistic-2.0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
URL: https://github.com/chencxxy28/MultiRD
BugReports: https://github.com/chencxxy28/MultiRD/issues
